comments: Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) legally disengages from Washington (CHA) and makes clean contact with the ball.
Rozier (CHA) makes marginal contact with Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) makes incidental contact with Washington (CHA) as he cleanly deflects the ball.
Washington (CHA) briefly places an arm to the front of Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) but the contact does not affect his FOM.  Gilgeous-Alexander's reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Washington (CHA) and Adams (OKC) engage and disengage as they move along the same path.
Adams (OKC) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Washington's (CHA) path.
After Ferguson (OKC) makes clean contact with the ball, he makes marginal contact with Rozier (CHA).
Rozier (CHA) takes a dribble after regaining possession of the ball after Ferguson (OKC) kicks it.  A kicked ball violation should have been whistled instead.
Adams (OKC) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Washington's (CHA) path.
Washington (CHA) and Adams (OKC) engage and disengage as they release from the pick.
Adams (OKC) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Washington's (CHA) path and does not deliver contact.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) avoids making contact with Washington (CHA) during his play at the basket.
Bridges (CHA) commits a take foul on Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).
Rozier (CHA) commits a take foul on Schroder (OKC).
Adams (OKC) establishes himself in a legal guarding position in Graham's (CHA) path and Graham loses his balance as he tries to move around Adams.
Zeller (CHA) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Ferguson's (OKC) path.
Adams (OKC) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Martin's (CHA) path.
Ferguson (OKC) firms up in Graham's (CHA) path during the pick and absorbs the contact.
Gilgeous-Alexander (CHA) releases the pass before he returns to the floor.
Zeller (CHA) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Schroder's (OKC) path.
Schroder (OKC) moves into Rozier's (CHA) space and makes contact to his leg that affects his jump shot attempt.
Adams (OKC) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Washington's (CHA) path.
Washington (CHA) places a forearm on Adams' (OKC) back during the rebound, but the contact is marginal.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) moves alongside Graham (CHA), but jumps from point A to point B into his body and the contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Zeller (OKC) delivers contact to Paul (OKC) that dislodges him from his offensive position.
Washington (CHA) makes marginal contact with Adams (OKC) as he tips the ball in.
Martin (CHA) commits a take foul on Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).
Ferguson (CHA) goes to, but not through Graham (CHA) and does not dislodge him from his position.
Ferguson (OKC) commits a take foul on Graham (CHA).
Schroder (OKC) makes incidental contact with Rozier (CHA) as Rozier stops and veers into Schroder's path.

Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the body contact from Washington (CHA) during his drive to the basket.  He then reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball.
Schroder (OKC) makes marginal contact with Graham (CHA) as they both attempt to retrieve the rebound.
